			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Private business letter from Manuel Alves Ferreira, a servant, to Francisco Pereira da Silva, his friend.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author states that he is ready to lend the addressee some money in case he sends him a receipt.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc"> The servant Manuel Alves Ferreira was accused of having robbed his master, Jacinto Fernandes da Costa Bandeira, a mayor.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
